&lt;h2 id="java-version-management">Java Version Management&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>How to switch between multiple installed versions of Java.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To check the available versions and the default environment, run:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>archlinux-java status
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Example output:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Copy code
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Available Java environments:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> java-11-temurin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> java-17-openjdk
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> java-18-openjdk (default)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> java-8-openjdk/jre
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>To set the default to java-11-temurin, use &lt;code>set&lt;/code>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo archlinux-java &lt;span style="color:#24909d">set&lt;/span> java-11-temurin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Verify the default with java -version:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ java -version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>openjdk version &amp;#34;11.0.16.1&amp;#34; 2022-08-12
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>OpenJDK Runtime Environment Temurin-11.0.16.1+1 (build 11.0.16.1+1)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM Temurin-11.0.16.1+1 (build 11.0.16.1+1, mixed mode)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>